eace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily,\u00a0Allah is merciful only to His servants who are merciful.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7448, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 923 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33444,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/ask-for-good-dunya-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":771,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Why not ask for good in this life and the Hereafter?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, visited a sick man among the Muslims and he was so emaciated that he was like thin bird. The Prophet said to him, \u201cHave you supplicated for anything or asked from Allah?\u201d The man said, \u201cYes. I said:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":45,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/26\/virtue-visiting-sick\/","url_meta":{"origin":771,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Vir